@startuml stm_primary
title <<stm>> CLightfieldTexture Primary State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<browse>> #e3f2fd
    BorderColor<<browse>>     #1565c0
    FontColor<<browse>>       #0d47a1
}
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

state "unbound" as Unbound <<browse>>
state "bound" as Bound <<browse>>

Unbound -down-> Bound : set_beam(B) [B != none]
Bound -up-> Unbound : set_beam(none)
Bound --> Bound : set_beam(B') [B' != none]\non_beam_changed

note right of Bound
    set_beam triggers initial render
    via explicit OnBeamChanged call.
    Subsequent CBeam mutations
    (gantry/couch/collim/jaws) fire
    GetChangeEvent which re-renders
    via the observer callback.
end note

@enduml
